Workflow Integration
1.) Capture Images: Use DigiCamControl or manual image capture.
2.) Process Images: Run the Python script to crop, enhance, and organize.
3.) Combine Images: Merge pages or generate PDFs.
4.) Extract Text (Optional): Use OCR for searchable PDFs or text exports.

----------------------------------------------------------

Scanning Workflow Directory
book_scanner_project/
