GUI Layout

+----------------------+-----------------------------------------+
| Book Scanner (Header Area)                                    |
+----------------------+-----------------------------------------+
| Settings (Sidebar) | Dynamic Content Area                     |
| - Capture Settings  | - Capture settings form (on click)      |
| - Processing        | - Processing settings form (on click)   |
| - PDF Settings      | - PDF settings form (on click)          |
| - Exit              |                                         |
+----------------------+-----------------------------------------+

